{
  "chapter": "062",
  "title": "管晏列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "管仲早年",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管仲\">夷吾（管仲）</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍上</span>人。年少时常常与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲍叔牙</span>交往，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>知道他<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>能。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>贫困，常常欺骗<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>始终很好地对待他，不因此而说什么。后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">公子小白（齐桓公）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子纠</span>。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">小白（齐桓公）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子纠</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>于内乱，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>禁。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>于是举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>被任用后，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国执掌<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span>因此称<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">霸</span>，九次会合<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">一匡天下</span>，这都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>的谋略。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "知己之恩",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>说:\"我当初困穷的时候，曾与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>一起做生意，分财利时多给自己，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>并不认为我<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贪</span>，知道我贫穷。我曾为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>谋事反而使他更加穷困，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>并不认为我<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">愚</span>，知道时机有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">利不利</span>。我曾三次出仕三次被<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逐</span>罢，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>并不认为我<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">不肖</span>，知道我没有遇上时机。我曾三次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>败逃跑，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>并不认为我<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">怯</span>懦，知道我有老<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子纠</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>亡时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召忽</span>为他<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>节，我却<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">幽囚</span>受辱，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>并不认为我无<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">耻</span>，知道我不以小节为羞，而<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">耻</span>于功名不显扬于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。生我的是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>，了解我的是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍子（鲍叔牙）</span>啊。\""
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "鲍叔让贤",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>之后，使自己地位居于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>之下。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>世世代代在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国享受<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">禄</span>位，有封邑的有<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多代（时长）</span>之久，常是有名的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>人不称赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>能，而称赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：鲍叔牙\">鲍叔（鲍叔牙）</span>能够识别人才。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "相齐称霸",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>担任<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>事做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国相后，凭借小小的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国地处海滨，流通货物、积累财富，使国家富足、军力强盛，与民俗同好同恶。所以他的主张说:\"<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">仓廪</span>充实才懂得<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼节</span>，衣食富足才知道<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">荣辱</span>，君上遵守法度则六亲关系牢固。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">四维</span>不张扬，国家就会灭亡。下令要像流水的源头一样自然，要顺应<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">民心</span>。\"因此政令平易而容易推行。百姓想要的，就顺从给予；百姓不愿意的，就顺从去除。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "因祸为福",
      "text": "他处理<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>事，善于把祸变为福，转<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">败</span>为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">功</span>。看重<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">轻重</span>之策，谨慎地运用<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">权衡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>实际上是因为恼怒<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少姬</span>，向南去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span>击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>便顺势<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，责问<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">包茅</span>不向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室进贡。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>实际上是向北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">征</span>讨<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">山戎</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>便顺势令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国重修<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>治。在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">柯</span>地的会盟上，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>想要背弃与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹沫</span>的盟约，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>便让他信守此约，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>由此都<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">归</span>附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。所以说:\"懂得给予就是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>得，这是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>治的宝贵之道。\""
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "管仲殁后",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>的富贵可比公室，有<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三归</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">反坫</span>的礼制，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人不认为他奢侈。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐国</span>遵循他的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>策，常常比<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>强盛。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百多年（时长）</span>后又出了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "晏子事君",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晏婴\">晏平仲（晏婴）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晏婴\">婴（晏婴）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莱</span>地<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夷维</span>人。他侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐灵公</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐庄公\">庄公（齐庄公）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐景公\">景公（齐景公）</span>，以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">节俭</span>和力行而受到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国的敬重。担任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国相后，吃饭不吃两样<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>食，妾不穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>衣。他在朝廷，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主问到他，就正直陈述；问不到他，就正直行事。国家有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>，就顺从君命；没有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>，就权衡君命。因此<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三世（时长）</span>显名于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "赎士知礼",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">越石父</span>是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>人，被捆缚在囚绳中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>外出时，在路上遇到他，解下左<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">骖</span>马赎了他，载他一同归来。没有告辞，就进入内室。过了很久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">越石父</span>请求与他绝交。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>吃惊地整理<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣冠</span>告谢说:\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晏婴\">婴（晏婴）</span>虽然不<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁</span>，使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span>于困厄，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>为什么要这么快就请求绝交呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：越石父\">石父（越石父）</span>说:\"不是这样。我听说<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>在不了解自己的人那里受委屈，在了解自己的人那里得信任。当我在囚绳之中时，那些人不了解我。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫子</span>既然感悟而赎了我，就是我的知己；既是知己却无<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼</span>待我，那确实不如身在囚绳之中。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>于是请他进来奉为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上客</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "御者自省",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国相，外出时，他车夫的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>子从门缝里窥视她的丈夫。她丈夫为国相驾车，拥着大<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">伞盖</span>，挥<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞭</span>驱驾四匹<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语·现代：扬扬自得\">扬扬甚自得（扬扬自得）</span>。回来后，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>子请求离去。丈夫问她缘故。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>子说:\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>身高不满<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六尺</span>，身为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐国</span>之相，名声显扬于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。今天我看他外出时，志向深沉，常常有自谦之意。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>身高<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八尺</span>，却给人做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">仆御</span>，然而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的神态却自以为满足，所以我请求离去。\"此后丈夫便自我克制谦抑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>觉得奇怪而问他，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御</span>夫如实回答。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>就推荐他做了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "读其遗书",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我读了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">管氏</span>的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">牧民</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">山高</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">乘马</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">轻重</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">九府</span>，以及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>，书中所言非常详尽啊。既然看过了他们的著作，就想观察他们的行事，因此编次了他们的传记。至于他们的书，世上多有流传，因此不再论述，只论其轶事。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "小管仲之意",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>世人称为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤臣</span>，然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>却看低他。难道是因为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>道衰微，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐桓公\">桓公（齐桓公）</span>既已<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>明，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>不勉励他达到<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王</span>道，反而称<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">霸</span>吗？俗语说:\"顺从发扬君主的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">美</span>德，匡救君主的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">恶</span>行，所以君臣上下才能相亲。\"难道不是说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管仲</span>这样的人吗？"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "晏子可慕",
      "text": "当<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>伏在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐庄公\">庄公（齐庄公）</span>尸体上哭泣，尽成<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼</span>节然后离去，难道就是所说的\"见到<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">义</span>而不去做就是没有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">勇</span>气\"的人吗？至于他劝谏陈说，冒犯<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主之颜，这就是所说的\"<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">进思尽忠，退思补过</span>\"的人啊！假使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晏子</span>还活着，即使让我为他执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞭</span>驾车，我也欣然仰慕他。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：管仲\">夷吾（管仲）</span>成就<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">霸</span>业，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晏婴\">平仲（晏婴）</span>被称为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤</span>人。仓廪充实粟米，饮食豆羹不掩肩。转祸为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">福</span>，危言而得以保全。孔子不用依赖左衽，太史公欣然愿执<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鞭</span>。成就<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼</span>节然后离去，人望犹存。"
    }
  }
}